title: Wentworth - S02E06 - The Pink Dragon.avi
description:
Wentworth - S02E06 - The Pink Dragon

Simmo struggles emotionally with the task given to her by Vinnie Holt - but she just can't bring herself to kill Bea in cold blood. Overwhelmed, she attempts suicide, only to be rescued by Bea herself, who ironically gives her the courage to go through with whatever she has to do to survive. Liz faces her greatest dilemma - to snitch or not to snitch.
